metadata.name: Crowded mind
metadata.description:
This is the beginning of the creation of my keybot world.
This is a show of my busy mind. When I paint, I enter another world whose characters are related to my feelings at that moment. If I feel good, happy characters are created, and if I am angry, evil characters are created.

This painting took me a long time and I emphasized the details so much that you have to look for some of them.
Look at the details, what attracted you at first glance?
